# TechCart - E-Commerce Website

TechCart is a Java based E-Commerce web application where users can browse products, add them to cart and place orders.

## Features

User Features
- User Registration
- Login & Logout
- Browse Products
- Add Products to Cart
- Update Cart Quantity
- Checkout Orders

Admin Features
- Add Products
- Update Products
- Remove Products
- Manage Inventory
- View Orders

## Technologies Used

Frontend
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Bootstrap

Backend
- Java
- Servlets
- JSP
- JDBC

Database
- MySQL

Server
- Apache Tomcat

